title: U.S. Supreme Court paves way for midterm redistricting in Texas in win for Trump, Republicans
description: The U.S. Supreme Court revived on Thursday a redrawn Texas electoral map designed to add more Republicans to the U.S. House of Representatives, boosting President Donald Trump's quest for his party to keep control of Congress in the 2026 midterm elections.
